name: Scared By Squares Demo
summary:
WARNING! Do not play if you are Scared By Squares

Scared by Squares is a creepy VR exploration game where you navigate liminal, cube-filled spaces that feel just a little too perfect. Something is off, and it’s getting worse.

Avoid roaming corrupted cubes, uncover hidden anomalies, and try to hold onto your sanity as the world slowly unravels around you. Play solo for a tense, immersive experience, or explore the unsettling halls with friends, if you think that will...
